{"tid":2208642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商界︰香港營商要靠邊站 選親共派或自由派令人無所適從","createTime":"2020-09-19T05:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T18:24:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":235,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"caee48e20368c5826b48f90533df1098c51c214f","tid":2208642,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:43:29.000Z","msg":"梁兆基︰香港不再是企業眼中營商樂土<br />\n<br />\n總商會總裁梁兆基在一個電台節目表示，限聚令冰封了不少微企的生意，對很多長久「被休業」的小商戶來說，政府的財政援助始終是杯水車薪，總商會最近對政府施政的問卷調查反映，不少企業最看重的是有效控制疫情，令業務重開，補助支援等都只屬次要。<br />\n<br />\n梁兆基又指，目前大小企業身處內外不斷的政治爭拗中，有些無所適從，而且動輒得咎，香港似乎已不再是企業眼中營商的樂土，不少企業最大的期盼是安穩的營商環境。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357951&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=4b0def43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357951</a>"},{"pid":"a55c66a042e58968ccae344edba875fd0e30eb59","tid":2208642,"uid":21545,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3410e7c18d7f19462ddc411f34f8de88d1ab5a41","tid":2208642,"uid":287422,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fe6291d8591bc642561de29650affa26af29e8","tid":2208642,"uid":33408,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"rep